@startuml LabSense Exam Taking Sequence

skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam roundcorner 5

title LabSense - Exam Taking Sequence

actor Student
participant Frontend
participant "Backend API" as Backend
database Database
participant "Judge0 API" as Judge0

== Student Login ==
Student -> Frontend: Login
Frontend -> Backend: POST /auth/login
Backend -> Database: Validate credentials
Database --> Backend: User data
Backend --> Frontend: JWT token
Frontend --> Student: Dashboard

== Start Exam ==
Student -> Frontend: Start exam
Frontend -> Backend: GET /exams/{id}
Backend -> Database: Fetch exam data
Backend -> Database: Fetch exam questions
Database --> Backend: Exam data
Backend --> Frontend: Exam data
Frontend --> Student: Display exam

== Submit Code ==
loop Multiple submissions
  Student -> Frontend: Submit code
  Frontend -> Backend: POST /submissions
  Backend -> Database: Store submission
  Backend -> Judge0: Execute code
  Judge0 --> Backend: Execution results
  Backend -> Database: Store results
  Backend --> Frontend: Score & feedback
  Frontend --> Student: Show results
end

== End Exam ==
Student -> Frontend: End exam
Frontend -> Backend: POST /sessions/end
Backend -> Database: Update session
Backend --> Frontend: Final score
Frontend --> Student: Exam completed

@enduml






